text: <!here> one of the challenges we are seeing here in the US is the shortage of ventilators. In Ethiopia even in normal times hospitals have short supply of ventilators and oxygen tanks and they normally use Ambu bags and where people manually by hand for hours. We need to think about how 1. we can get more ambu bags and 2. Ways to miminize manual meaning replace the human hand with some machine hand. We of course need electrical and mechanical engineers to make it happen.
